## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the scope of sources consulted. Some sources may not reflect the most current statistics or developments in air pollution research. Additionally, the focus was primarily on global impacts, which may overlook region-specific issues and solutions. Further research could provide more localized insights and recent data.